title: Midnight Bloom
description: A deep, intoxicating floral scent with hints of amber and sandalwood. Perfect for evening wear.

title: Coastal Breeze
description: A fresh, aquatic fragrance with notes of sea salt, lemon zest, and white tea. Ideal for daily use.

title: Spiced Vanilla Dream
description: Warm and inviting, featuring creamy vanilla, cinnamon, and a touch of patchouli. A comforting winter favorite.

title: Gardenia Grace
description: A classic, elegant scent dominated by pure gardenia, tuberose, and green leaves. Timeless femininity.

title: Sultan's Oud
description: Rich and powerful oud wood blended with saffron and rose. A luxurious and long-lasting unisex fragrance.

title: Citrus Sunrise
description: An energizing blend of mandarin, grapefruit, and bergamot. A vibrant, uplifting scent for the morning.

title: Leather & Smoke
description: A rugged, bold fragrance with sharp leather, smoky cedar, and a hint of cardamom. Distinctly masculine.

title: Pink Peony Petals
description: Light, airy, and youthful with dominant notes of peony, red apple, and jasmine. Perfect for spring.

title: Forest Rain
description: An earthy, clean aroma capturing the scent of a forest after a fresh rain, with moss and damp wood.

title: Golden Honey Amber
description: Sweet, deep, and comforting. A blend of warm honey, golden amber, and musk for a cozy feeling.
